* Snow Tech grinned and saluted her.*

" Yes ma'am, sir, ma'am!"

* He then turned to Shadow Cat and began to march off into the bush, intent 
on getting to the base. Shadow cat rolled her eyes and sighed*

" He always manages to make some stupid remark out of anything and 
everything!"

* She runs ahead of him barring his way*

" You stupid ass! it would take too long to walk! Get your ass back there so 
i can air lift your fat ass to our new home!"

* He saluted her and spun on his heel, facing the way he came and marched 
back to his original position, facing Iron Raptor. He looked at her with 
twinkeling eyes and spread his arms so Shadow Cat could lift him. Shadow Cat 
graspe dunder his arms and spread her wings, lifting her and Snow Tech off 
the ground about nine feet. She spoke to Iron Raptor before she took off 
totally.*

" We will meet you there, i'm sure that we can come up with some thing to at 
least tip the odds to our side."

* And with that spooken, she lifted herself and the white bot off into the 
sky, but not before Snow Techs smart assed remark came down to the other 
twos ears.*

" This is little kitties airlines, we are ready for take off, over. Yes, you 
are cleared for take off little kitty. Thank-you mission control, rodger 
that. Vrooom!!! Last one there is a over-sized scrap heap!"

* His giggling annoyed Shadow Cat and she was tempted to threaten him with 
bodily harm , but knew that would give him the satisfaction of getting her 
goat, so she kept her mouth shut and steered off to the left sharply so he 
squealed like a little girl. She smiled and headed to the base at full 
speed.*
